title: Ebro In The Morning - Legend Jackie Joyner-Kersee + Queens Assemblywoman Alicia Hyndman
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/11.

Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (00:30, & 25:00). Track & field athlete and American Legend Jackie Joyner-Kersee talks about Noami Osaka and Queens Assemblywoman Alicia Hyndman discusses Juneteenth. 

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
